infinite:
theorem Icc.infinite : Infinite (Icc a b) :=

#align Icc.infinite Icc.infinite
Ioo_infinite:
theorem Ioo_infinite : (Ioo a b).infinite :=

#align Ioo_infinite Ioo_infinite

Ioc_infinite:
